{"tid":613561,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"返工第一日，我已計劃讀Master了","createTime":"2018-04-01T18:18:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-04T07:35:59.000Z","uid":62324,"like":2,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"0e31249bb238685e51d98bbc869cc8cf8ba8da0f","tid":613561,"uid":62324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T18:18:29.000Z","msg":"我好慶幸可以係Year 2搵到份intern，令我知道讀書既世界係幾咁單純，可以話無憂無慮，同時都明白身在職場多險詐。<br />\n<br />\n返第一日工已經想返去繼續讀書，我認我係怕收工收得夜/怕由低做起/怕一星期做六日。所以我計劃定可能畢業後做2至3年野，之後再讀個1年既Master當Break仔放。<br />\n<br />\n希望返緊工既大家可以比小小意見我，例如咩Master易入易出/ 去英國讀Master有咩好介紹/ 返工返多10年8載先再諗Master<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bdfca849b560aad6f1bc596105a08fed291d4ee","tid":613561,"uid":28052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T18:22:53.000Z","msg":"本身讀咩先<br />\n易入易出就緊係business marketing 個堆"},{"pid":"ce2d1ea25377120680a0da73dfe093dbdf7f0e12","tid":613561,"uid":62324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6bdfca849b560aad6f1bc596105a08fed291d4ee","tid":613561,"uid":28052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T18:22:53.000Z","msg":"本身讀咩先<br />\n易入易出就緊係business marketing 個堆"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T18:27:49.000Z","msg":"我本身讀BBA<br />\n多謝提點"},{"pid":"b96f3caed6bc9a6f6b385e1514d3732a3c72ff9a","tid":613561,"uid":63440,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T18:58:12.000Z","msg":"讀完1年之後咪一樣要返工<br />\n你屋企好有錢既無問題<br />\n無錢既, 你都係諗清楚, 唔好為逃避而讀, 你讀完個master都唔代表可以唔洗OT收夜"},{"pid":"62dc2d23c6c2513cf5f3c125157768d4a4c636dc","tid":613561,"uid":164130,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T19:03:00.000Z","msg":"海外讀完master再留當地工作幾年後入籍移民...不過BBA搵相關既工都唔容易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 除非入finance果d工...."},{"pid":"8fa3e03f7274d42a6a9890bcf12e20076c553dcf","tid":613561,"uid":152340,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T19:05:11.000Z","msg":"On9, 